queries.sql: SELECT rise_users.id, rise_users.user_type, rise_users.is_admin, rise_users.role_id, rise_users.email, rise_users.first_name, rise_users.last_name, rise_users.image, rise_users.message_checked_at, rise_users.notification_checked_at, rise_users.client_id, rise_users.enable_web_notification, rise_users.is_primary_contact, rise_users.sticky_note, rise_roles.title as role_title, rise_roles.permissions, (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(id) team_ids FROM rise_team WHERE FIND_IN_SET('1', `members`)) as team_ids FROM rise_users LEFT JOIN rise_roles ON rise_roles.id = rise_users.role_id AND rise_roles.deleted = 0 WHERE rise_users.deleted=0 AND rise_users.id=1
